snippet.title: Everyone's Platinum Disco
snippet.description:
They said I could mashup whatever I wanted in Platinum Disco...

So I decided to mashup everything.

Song sources are found in the annotations

All pics and the mashup (mp3/flac) are in: http://www.mediafire.com/?l803ykp6pyudcfk

Thanks Antsants for arranging the .rar, Ed for the name/fixing the Renai Circulation timing, and r/a/dio for streaming it
